snippet.title: The Political Machine 2016 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The Political Machine official game site: http://www.politicalmachine.com

Run for President of the United States as one of over a dozen presidential candidates or create your own ideal candidate. Give speeches, go on talk shows, hire unsavory operatives, and do whatever it takes to win on election day.

Developed and published by Stardock: http://www.stardock.com/

***
Find us on http://Twitch.tv/stardock
Streaming live all your favorite games and more!
